commits.author: Robert Muir
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Returns a List of keys that almost match the argument key. * Keys returned will have exactly diff characters that do not match the * target key, where diff is equal to the last value passed in as an argument * to the setMatchAlmostDiff method. *

* If the matchAlmost method is called before the * setMatchAlmostDiff method has been called for the first time, * then diff = 0. * *@param key * The target key. *@return A List with the results. */ public List matchAlmost(String key) { return matchAlmost(key, defaultNumReturnValues); }
